reviewText: love the music just not great dancers
Excellent my husband says. Good music disc. Would recommend it to others. Enjoy it and will share it with my soon.

I first saw Pavlo in a little restaurant in Birmingham Al. They were just passing through and stopped in to play. It was right after the release of His Fantasia cd. We were blown away. Since, I have introduced many people to them. I just got the Mediterranean Nights DVD. It is absolutely incredible. The talent, skill, and raw emotional. Unbelievable. It is truly a must see. Brian Richmond Virginia
Pavlo shows his love for the guitar and he is unparalled in his field.  Have seen him live and his performances are warm and entertaining.
